ewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>結果</h2>\n<p>測定結果は 2 つ載せておく</p>\n<h3 id=\"dart-run\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dart-run\" aria-label=\"dart run permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>dart run</h3>\n<p><code>dart run</code>では for と for-in はほぼ同速度。for が速かったり、for-in の方が速かったり実行のたびに変わる。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">for</th>\n<th align=\"center\">for-in</th>\n<th align=\"center\">foreach</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3150658us</td>\n<td align=\"center\">3492088us</td>\n<td align=\"center\">8578483us</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3406944us</td>\n<td align=\"center\">3226942us</td>\n<td align=\"center\">8003298us</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"dart-compile\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dart-compile\" aria-label=\"dart compile permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\"